quot;>;我们最喜欢的机器人吸尘器&lt;/a>;。&lt;/ p>; &lt;p id=&quot;X7SSHw&quot;>;像往常一样，我们将搜索亚马逊的登陆...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24255302/amazon-prime -day-deals-tips-news-guide-2024-october&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24255302/amazon-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide-2024-october" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24255302/amazon-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide-2024-october</id><author><name>边缘员工</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T09:22:49-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T09:22:49-04:00</updated><title>您可以在我们的一些家庭办公室首选产品上获得最佳 Prime Day 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;带转角办公桌和绿色照明的家庭办公室。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-X4TJRG_RqVw0xic1vJgaw9n_N4=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73641948/247212_WOYD_JW_JWeatherbed_00 13.0.jpg&quot; / >; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Jess Weatherbed / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;GMvhi6&quot;>;本网站上最喜欢的系列之一 - 至少就我们的许多员工而言 - 是&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22340755/whats-on-your-desk-setup-tech-verge&quot;>;“你的桌子上有什么？”&lt;/a>;我们在其中查看家庭工作区&lt;em>;The Verge&lt;/em>; 的一些人。 （一方面，令人欣慰的是，我们大多数人都有同样的杂乱综合症，而且这是在清理照片空间之后的情况！）&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float -left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;NS22NB&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The您可以在我们最喜欢的一些小工具上获得最佳 Prime Day 优惠“，”url“：”https://www.theverge.com/24265074/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sale-tech-staff-picks- favorites-october-2024&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;亚马逊 Prime Day 第二天可以买到的最优惠商品&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/ amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;2MtZjQ&quot;>;我们检查了是否我们在员工的家庭办公室设置中发现的任何有趣的东西——办公椅、灯串、绘图板等——都在今年秋季的亚马逊 Prime Day 活动期间出售，我们想出了这些。&lt;/p >; &lt;h3 id=&quot;uQy0MU&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24259381/work-home-desk-logitech-sony&quot;>;&lt;em>;David Pierce，特约编辑&lt;/ em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;/h3>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;a93TTt&quot;>;一把舒适的办公椅&lt;/h2>; &lt;div id=&quot;1Xny3W&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard:12447883&quot;>;&lt;/ div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;pZpbuA&quot;>;我只需在亚马逊上查找该名称：它是“&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B06Y3PGPR2/?tag= theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;HON 办公椅黑色 |点火2.0 |符合人体工程学...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24265605/amazon-prime-day-deals-home-office-wfh-desk-accessories- sale-october-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24265605/amazon-prime-day-deals-home-office-wfh-desk-accessories-sale-october-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24265605/amazon-prime-day-deals-home-office-wfh-desk-accessories-sale-october-2024</id><author><name>芭芭拉·克拉斯诺夫</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T09:19:29-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T09:19:29-04:00</updated><title>任天堂正在制作一款闹钟，这样你就可以在塞尔达传说和超级马里奥的声音中醒来</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;任天堂 Alarmo 闹钟的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4AhMmGzoz-5eWsCzABH5xvkukg8=/0x1:3500x2334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73641941/NSC_Alarmo_6.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：任天堂&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;BgkzMJ&quot;>;这不是&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24051677/nintendo-switch-2-pro -rumors-news&quot;>;Switch 的继任者&lt;/a>;，但任天堂确实推出了一款新硬件：动作控制闹钟。该设备名为 Alarmo，它“对你的动作做出反应”，这意味着你可以通过手势让它小睡，或者通过实际起床来停止它。它的售价为 99.99 美元，将于 2025 年初上市，不过任天堂表示 Switch Online 订户可以 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/nintendo-sound-clock-alarmo-121311/&quot; >;现在就尽早购买&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;3HfJyF&quot;>;看来这是&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/23/24251736/ nintendo-mmwave-device-24ghz-fcc-filing&quot;>;上个月向联邦通信委员会提交的神秘任天堂小工具&lt;/a>;，该委员会透露该设备具有 2.4GHz Wi-Fi 无线电和 24GHz 毫米波传感器。除了运动功能之外，该设备的一个重要部分似乎是其身临其境的声音，这些声音来自五种不同的......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2024/10/9/24265984/nintendo-alarmo-alarm-clock-date-price&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24265984/nintendo-alarmo-alarm-clock-date-price" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24265984/nintendo-alarmo-alarm-clock-date-price</id><author><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T09:19:08-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T09:19:08-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊 10 月 Prime Day 促销中我们最喜欢的 50 美元以下优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;充电盒顶部的一对回声耳机&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/cMZsgRPD9nD35Nm1bsBrADpVJjA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73639696/cwelch_20210511_4582_0011.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;具有 ANC 和无线充电功能的第二代 Amazon Echo Buds 目前仅需 45 美元。 &lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;iZ4p4h&quot;>;我们正处于亚马逊今年第二个 Prime Day 活动的第二天，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/2024/9/17/24244180/amazon-october-prime-day-big-deal-days-fall-dates-2024&quot;>;Prime 大优惠日&lt;/a>;持续至 10 月 9 日。虽然命名惯例可能很糟糕，但销售却并非如此。事实上，我们最喜欢的许多小工具和商品现在都在享受显着的折扣，我们在更大的综述中强调了这一点&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon -prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024&quot;>;黄金日最佳优惠&lt;/a>;。然而，如果您想控制预算，您可以在这里找到我们 50 美元以下的首选。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;TUx507&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;100 美元以下可获得的最佳 10 月 Prime Day 优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24264356/amazon-prime-day-best- Cheap-tech-deals-under-100-october-2024&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;如何在亚马逊秋季 Prime Day 促销期间找到最优惠的价格&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com /21502865/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-how-to-find&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您可以在我们最喜欢的一些小工具上获得的最佳 Prime Day 优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/24265074/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sale-tech-staff-picks-favorites-october-2024&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div >; &lt;p id=&quot;1dZhWj&quot;>;下面，我们精选了一些我们可以亲自担保的低于 50 美元的商品。当然，它们包括许多亚马逊自己的设备，包括 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/all-new-amazon-fire-tv-stick-4k-max/dp/B0BP9SNVH9?tag=theverge02 -20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Fire TV Stick 4K Max&lt;/a>;，最新&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Echo-Spot-TP-Link -Smart-Color/dp/B0DF15V76B?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Echo Spot&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com /Amazon-smart-plug-works-with-Alexa/dp/B089DR29T6?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊便宜的智能插头&lt;/a>;。我们的非亚马逊设备上还有很多值得注意的优惠...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best- Cheap-tech-deals-under-50-october-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-50-october-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24262440/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-50-october-2024</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T09:18:10-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T09:18:10-04:00</updated><title>卡西欧将经典数字手表放大，打造出这款复古台钟</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;卡西欧台钟，看起来像经典卡西欧数字手表的放大版。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/_UKyc224neCTCpKsI558oWpPBog=/0x0:1344x896/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73641937/casio1.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;这款台钟的灵感来自经典的卡西欧数字手表，但包含附加功能。&lt;/em>; |图片：卡西欧日本&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;pMuYN0&quot;>;卡西欧日本正在发布一款新的台钟，对于那些放弃智能手表而青睐更简单的数字手表的人来说，这款时钟会很熟悉。这是一个 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.casio.com%2Fjp%2Fwatches%2Fcasio%2Fclock%2Fproduct.DQD -851J-8%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F10%2F9%2F24265964%2Fcasio-digital-watch-desk-a158w-clock-japan-retro -vintage&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https 的超大版本&lt;/a>; %3A%2F%2Fwww.casio.com%2Fca-en%2Fwatches%2Fcasio%2Fproduct.A158WA-1%2F&amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F10 %2F9%2F24265964%2Fcasio-digital-watch-desk-a158w-clock-japan-retro-vintage&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Casio A158W&lt;/a>; 数字手表，可以成为一款很棒的手表床头柜闹钟，尽管您可能不想在卧室里隐藏它的复古魅力。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;4rqoxS&quot;>;该时钟的正式名称为 DQD-851J-8JF，将于 10 月开始在日本独家发售25 日售价 4,378 日元（约合 29 美元）。这甚至比卡西欧 A158W 手表还要便宜，因为该时钟是由塑料而不是不锈钢制成的。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;q0iJiU&quot;>;这款座钟还没有秒表和在每小时整点响起的报时声。但添加了卡西欧基本数字手表上没有的功能，例如温度计和...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24265964/casio- digital-watch-desk-a158w-clock-japan-retro-vintage&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24265964/casio-digital-watch-desk-a158w-clock-japan-retro-vintage" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24265964/casio-digital-watch-desk-a158w-clock-japan-retro-vintage</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry></feed>